text: Maria Schutzmeier (born 29 October 1999) is a Nicaraguan swimmer. She competed in the women's 100 metre freestyle at the 2019 World Aquatics Championships. ==References== Category:1999 births Category:Living people Category:Nicaraguan female swimmers Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Swimmers at the 2019 Pan American Games Category:Female freestyle swimmers
